betterquesting:10.desc:8:
If you're to make your way towards the Steam Age, you'll want a hefty stock of resources to supplement your escapades.

All the listed resources in this quest will be crucial, and we recommend you try going above and beyond what we ask for here, as you'll reduce the amount of times you need to go out to gather more.

Having trouble locating Rubber trees? You can find them more commonly in Swamp biomes.
